"This is your WordPress site description (tagline) — it is optional and you "
"can change it anytime from the wp-admin dashboard."
msgstr ""
"ນີ້ແມ່ນຄຳອະທິບາຍເວັບໄຊ WordPress ຂອງທ່ານ (ຄຳຂວັນ) — ຈະໃສ່ຫຼືບໍ່ໃສ່ກໍໄດ້ "
